{"tid":683703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾挺「台灣是國家」 好市多(Costco) 進上海恐遭抵制","createTime":"2018-05-30T02:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T04:32:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19d7a5ab2f510eaf3ebd925f334603b1b0ba1781","tid":683703,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"即將入駐上海浦東的美國連鎖超市Costco（台灣稱「好市多」，大陸稱「開市客」），日前被大陸民眾檢舉有支持台獨傾向，好市多的中國合作企業&mdash;上海浦東康橋（集團）有限公司昨天發函敦促好市多母公司回應。<br />\n<br />\n中共黨媒人民日報海外版官網海外網廿二日報導，一名從上海到美國留學、畢業後留在美國工作的馬姓民眾爆料指出，好市多二○一六年曾發過一封致歉信表示「台灣是一個國家」，最近臉書（Facebook）上有人又舊事重提。<br />\n<br />\n據海外網報導，馬姓民眾提到的致歉信是「台灣人公共事務會和賴言厚及梁靖偉」，於二○一六年四月廿日在臉書發布的一則訊息：「我們經常給各個企業、政府機構和組織寫信，制止對方在提及台灣時，使用『是中國的一個省』這樣的表述。上個月，我們發現，在Costco的網上招聘啟事中，台灣被列入『省份』而不是『國家』選項。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣人公共事務會（FAPA）時任主席陳彼得為此寫信抗議。FAPA後來收到好市多人力資源和風險管理高級副總裁卡蘭（Patrick Callans）的致歉信。<br />\n<br />\n信中承認，國家列表中沒有台灣這一選項純屬疏忽，將盡快修正。並說明好市多在台灣有分店，認同「台灣是一個國家」。<br />\n<br />\n海外網報導，上述消息引發中國網友關注，要求好市多公司以及康橋集團給中國消費者一個說法。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，上海國有企業康橋集團行政部楊姓主管表示，相關人員廿三日一早就先電話聯繫好市多業務部人員。康橋並著手起草函文，中午在未收到對方任何回應的情況下，康橋集團招商服務部代表集團向好市多公司正式發函。<br />\n<br />\n同時，康橋集團向上級指導部門&mdash;上海浦東新區商務委員會進行匯報溝通，希望在政府的支持下，敦促好市多回應此事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/11323/3161351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F11323%2F3161351&d=5kzrlEfzlIokQJ1uteSlYzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8a62311d\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/11323/3161351</a>"},{"pid":"349cf3df47363f678bc1fb5b353b4c5eaf8af829","tid":683703,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio @marcorubio<br />\n 4h4 hours ago<br />\n<br />\nHere we go again. @Costco is latest U.S. company facing threats from #China for its stance on #Taiwan It should trouble all Americans that we have companies &amp; people in our country being censored by the Chinese govt with threat of losing access to market"},{"pid":"282b3539382351774372ae45747c0795d15becdd","tid":683703,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:24:06.000Z","msg":"一名從上海到美國留學、畢業後留在美國工作的馬姓民眾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正宗支那人"},{"pid":"93d479248cb639803e1d13c1b2990223e2a534e1","tid":683703,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"咪住先<br />\n身為中國人點解會上FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52151f3c8aa07083948ac9186435f216f2914e66","tid":683703,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"支那人真係煩"},{"pid":"4dadeb03fba98204fe4ab9c3c6c2f9a0565f2dd8","tid":683703,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93d479248cb639803e1d13c1b2990223e2a534e1","tid":683703,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"咪住先<br />\n身為中國人點解會上FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"身在美國，心在中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432b2aa83656f6b95e1561028d503471983ec400","tid":683703,"uid":156005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:32:25.000Z","msg":"一名從上海到<strong>美國留學</strong>、畢業後留在<strong>美國工作的</strong>馬姓民眾爆料指出，好市多二○一六年曾發過一封致歉信表示「台灣是一個國家」，<strong>最近臉書（Facebook）</strong>上有人又舊事重提。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢位馬姓民眾真係心在中國身在美國既典型愛國撚"},{"pid":"f0b5096bbdb8c96a0515c9f63aff82b95cd57f30","tid":683703,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"你加關稅<br />\n我台報復"},{"pid":"d0c5f60aa4f543aba5190f13214a62e78e96f548","tid":683703,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"結果：首日開業多人到要停業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛國喎"}]}